Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直戴着那个发饰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由算是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是没啥理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记带数学的笔记了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天有数学课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦  不是还有作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家去取一趟  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正作业也没做  带不带都一样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍然是印尼语早安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.63,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,300)\fad(600,200)}日\N常\N之\N9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了出现了出现了…麻衣老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这莫非就是必杀技之「招呼保留」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大气非凡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像山一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  就像山一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…实际上是不是已经不止山的程度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  和山是没有一丁点关系就是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  麻衣生气的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我昨天把麻衣便当里的西兰花吃了的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就买来啦  西兰花～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了后我才知道麻衣最喜欢西兰花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我一直觉得自己做了不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也不是西兰花的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜花？看来也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我做的错事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她是为了哪件而生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心里大概有数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就只能老实向她道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  昨天吃了你的主菜真对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了兔子苹果  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你的饭  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到只剩黑豆了  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为昨天午饭的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非是更早之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麻衣抽屉里放着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨像的头折断的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是之后擅自把佛像带回家的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是偷偷地把佛像埋进土里的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:03.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}便条：对不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是后来改变主意  在麻衣的桌子上供奉神像的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进一步想想  难道是丢进焚化炉里烧了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  麻衣你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么啊  原来是在听音乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你才会不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道  一个人在那里自言自语地说个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险  差点就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半部分的事  我第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你的发型  是不是稍微违反了学校里的风纪规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃铜锣烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:16.04,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  还要写讲义  我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离数学课还有五分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天已经借美绪的作业抄过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一生的请求！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  果然就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀  忘记做数学作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就借我抄一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  Thanks  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦  我会以超马赫速度抄完的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  超级大迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账东西  早上开始就在吵什么吵  正雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我超级大迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被裁员了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  那个  这个好像和数学讲义有些出入…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会请你喝果汁的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课迟到了  老爸也被裁员了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一边都糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做这种事的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正雄岂不是糟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来正雄会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是生死攸关的时候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我讲义啦  麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这样了  我会请你吃车站前面的那个的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  这个  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这不是有的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点拿出来啦  麻衣个坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就以超快速度开抄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的那张讲义  是什么时候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去新奥尔良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题  有没有会解的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有够难的啊  赤城的课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记做作业  就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答错问题的话  又会让他生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话讲在前面  没干劲的家伙们我会马上记录在成绩单上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这一招吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会就这么被你吓倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.55,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N11
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是23号  我就点座号23号的中之条…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手抽筋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这时候手抽筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这样下去的话会进入他视野的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先逃向死角  向死角…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子  椅子被挪动了呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什么声音  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有谁的手机响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信谢礼～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一幕哟  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫做「全班笑得开了花」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个问题  相生你来回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！  咻啪啪啪啪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻啪啪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:04.52,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N12
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  砂糖和牛奶都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没有忘记买的东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天的鸡蛋可真便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我也买了一堆呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了  今天是鸡蛋的特卖会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢  虽然还能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是回店里一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑猫先生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…我不能养你呢  都已经有博士在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  随便带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…但是好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才不是这个问题呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  难道不可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  可爱是可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  喂养小动物就要费心去照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你办的到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会帮你哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫它的排泄物你也得做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃什么都不打算帮忙的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就不给你摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！  那…那可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了  不是那个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士  博士  睡着了哦  这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔顺哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士好狡猾  我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子的毛也好柔顺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子两边也好柔顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边的肉球好柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边的也好柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴的毛也好柔顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尾巴  它耳朵里面的毛才柔顺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  但是摸起来的感觉  尾巴更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴才不柔顺呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  是不是哪里痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了「说话围巾」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哆啦A梦哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好厉害  但也太快了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快让阪本戴上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫叫阪本吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  箱子上也这么写的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  真是廉价的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就会说话了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说话哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想  你们刚才都摸得太过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说  猫会叫个不停几乎都是因为肚子饿了的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  我不知道这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为箱子上写着「阪本」  这也太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我就说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都多少岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我8岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃的制造年龄是1年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我1岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照人类的年龄来算的话可是有20岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫我「阪本先生」才对头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:18.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大阪腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对头…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  以后能吃到免费的饭我是很感激啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过希望你们能够谨记对长辈的那份尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句  你们给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定抱有「因为是猫就能随便摸」这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可说清楚了  虽然我不讨厌被随便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  猫有着自己的限度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它放回原来那个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.32,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,270)\fad(600,0)}草\N\N\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我付了房租还给我吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困难就要互相关照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有别的需要的话  不要客气  直接说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  稍微借我点钱…随便说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得意忘形的日文是「天狗になる」字面意思就是「变成天狗」…冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  稍微对你好点你就得意忘形了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:45.40,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)\bord10\shad0\be50\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}草\N人\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教…教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像误会什么了  校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它身体的部分打开来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:14.93,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N13
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了的话  车站前的那个就作废了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁一局定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  麻衣  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你是不是有点抢跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  确实是有点早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那样一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧   是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当做没看见  我们再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么重新摆好姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻视了对手的握力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  这样一来热身运动也做够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀  这可真是相当难缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  但是我无论身心都开始热起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该动…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真格的了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我走神了  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我居然连续三次大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  是是  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看到了  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初心者的好运就到此为止了哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地来决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  这不是很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫扳手腕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我稍微保管一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久没有拿出全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我差不多一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不认真的话  我也认真不起来了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  下次才是真真正正的决战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要使出必杀技了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个破扳手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变得那么热血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我忘记去上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉一开始就不怎么对劲呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  车站前面的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和23瓶果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手抽筋而且没有做讲义还被骂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  结果正雄他会怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了啦  我再追加一瓶果汁给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳豆激酶这名  有没有让人想吐槽这是什么笑点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这激酶算什么啊  是小夜曲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(255,340)}Kinase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(436,340)}Serenade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下回的日常是第4话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
