Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}现在才第一次发觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小时满脑子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意识不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:08.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}觉得与平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:07.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:11.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:14.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:12.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N情\N相\N悦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:16.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  视线和他对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:20.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么什么  这种忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:26.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:32.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那种事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:36.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感觉都要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急转直下的我的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼间  脸像着火般变得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎么可能  我的手居然在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是所谓的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  说话咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我语无伦次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你对我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:55.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N对\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:59.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:02.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:08.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
